Cassper Nyovest is too disciplined and essentially too busy to meet Beyonce this weekend. Have you ever? Welcome to the We Can’t Believe What Cassper Just Said club. Thousands of Twitter users are dying of shock and laughter after Caspper said he was invited to an event where he probably would’ve met Beyonce but he declined. “I was invited to go Watch Beyonce this weekend but I have to work,” the tweet said. “The crazy thing is, I was invited by the lead singer of one of the biggest bands in world, I probably would’ve met Beyonce through him. I almost packed my bags and left but the way my self discipline is setup,” he continued. Needless to say, he has now become the butt of a joke that has turned into a challenge which is slowly gaining momentum on Twitter.  